description: Nordic Waterproofing Holding AB produces and supplies waterproofing products and services for buildings and infrastructure. The company is headquartered in Helsingborg, Skane and currently employs 1,083 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2020-11-30. The firm operates through its brands, such as AL-Katot, Distri Pond, Hetag Tagmaterialer, Kerabit, KerabitPro, LA Kattohuolto, Mataki, Nordic Takvard, Nortett, Phonix Tag Materialer, RVT, SealEco, SPT-Painting, Taasinge Elementer, Trebolit and Veg Tech. Nordic Waterproofing offers building products, EPDM products, green infrastructure and prefabricated Elements. The Groups operates in Denmark, Finland, Latvia, Norway and Sweden.
